HEADWORD: Unruled
<hw>Un*ruled"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
governed or controlled.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Unruled</xex> and
undirected.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not ruled or marked with lines; <as>as,
<ex>unruled</ex> paper</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unruliment</ent>⟦br⟧
